divs: Sighting DetailsI just got my Motorola Android phone and I was playing around in Google maps. At address 2036 W 160th St Gardena Ca. I was looking at the location and in the sky is a unknown object. It is not the sun because it is on the other side. I don't think it's a street light because it's too far away from a pole. Anyone with google maps can go to this address and look for themselves and come to their own conclusions.
